data.description: Well maintained home situated on a private lot in Marine Hills Neighborhood! This home is 5 bedroom with 2.5 bath, Updated kitchen with cherry cabinets, granite counters & SS appliances, Open concept living room with hardwood flooring & wood burning Fireplace, Primary bdrm features a walk-in closet with its own private walk-in shower, Fully fenced backyard with patio & garden space. Close proximity to Redondo Beach, Wooten Park, Salty's, Shopping centers, Schools, Hwy & I5.
